{"tid":1537811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共媒：龍應台美化暴力，只見雞蛋，而不見燃燒彈？","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:56:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"29f9f34b274cfc83a812880e8d1a19f1d322937d","tid":1537811,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"台灣著名作家龍應台日前在Facebook發表對反修例風波的看法，以「花園的地上有一顆雞蛋」形容香港，指如把香港當敵人以武力對付，恐怕不是香港背叛了「祖國」，而是「祖國」背叛了香港。<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒《人民日報》刊文反駁，批評龍應台試圖營造出一種「以卵擊石」的悲情，為何只見雞蛋，而不見燃燒彈。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，號稱文化人的龍應台的邏輯，其實早被大陸網民看穿，當你和她談止暴制亂，她卻和你談情懷，那就是思維上的狡猾。<br />\n<br />\n文章又批評龍應台把普通香港青年與暴力極端分子混為一談，美化了暴力，不問是非，強調中央所做的一切都是為了香港好，不希望極盡「攬炒」綁架獅子山下大多數矢志奮進的人，才是對香港最大的尊重與愛惜。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241437/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2241437%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Hs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=66f2696b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241437/</a>"},{"pid":"7237f65d99a59880bcce94ffed8ac286c7e82902","tid":1537811,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27c78a88f5401f5b53c808f8801a075d6a5ea40f","tid":1537811,"uid":230890,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30dc1ca1dd594f77974ebcbbb4b5b81406ecfcfa","tid":1537811,"uid":207195,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"燃燒彈咁勁，你用水炮車同我地交換囉"},{"pid":"f491554382f7f899582a825163a648178c17e512","tid":1537811,"uid":3775,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"真係得啖笑 <br />\n當年坦克車係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0274cd37b887c0f9f40e49ce054d4ef487f0fd","tid":1537811,"uid":53687,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"見到，差佬掟燃燒彈丫嘛"},{"pid":"9494dd81ddb4c2bcdfd89dddaa914260a67b4bce","tid":1537811,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41626bb6962cc1570e03f2c5db0252f33ba67d52","tid":1537811,"uid":41245,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"